org.ow2.easywsdl.wsdl.test.util

Class BaseWSDLSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.easywsdl.wsdl.test.util.BaseWSDLSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.woden.WSDLSource

    public class BaseWSDLSource
extends Object
implements org.apache.woden.WSDLSource
    This abstract class implements methods of the WSDLSource interface that are common across all concrete implementations.

    The only method on this interface that is specific to each concrete implementation is the setSource method and this method is declared abstract on this class.

    Author:
    John Kaputin (jkaputin@apache.org)
